<item>
            <title>[LU-19423] Improve garbage collection in changelogs further</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19423</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently changelog garbage collection could be optimized further, one significant change would be to begin regularly warning in system / console logging that changelogs have hit certain thresholds (e.g. changelog using 20% MDT free space usage, 22%, 24%, ...) to allow the administrators to easily know from existing logging that the garbage collection process may begin soon and or that there are consumers which are lagging or not consuming.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
